{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "07", "m": "11", "Y": "2025"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "11", "S": "33"}}, "news": [{"title": "Unauthorised layouts mushroom near Mulapeta port", "para": "The under-construction Mulapeta Port in Srikakulam has fueled a real estate boom, leading to numerous unauthorized land layouts. Realtors are allegedly converting agricultural land into plots without proper permissions, often failing to provide basic amenities. Many buyers are being lured by promises of high returns on plots in these unapproved ventures.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/real-estate-scandal-unauthorised-layouts-surge-near-mulapeta-port/125154878?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-210387/125154878.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Andhra Pradesh: APMDC plans to acquire more land for beach sand mining", "para": "Andhra Pradesh Mineral Development Corporation is seeking an additional 5,000 hectares for beach sand mining in Srikakulam, following the Centre's earlier allocation of 1,000 hectares. With operations underway, APMDC is pushing for the next phase. Some proposed sites are in reserve forests, requiring compensatory afforestation. APMDC plans to use previously acquired land for this purpose.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/andhra-pradesh-apmdc-to-expand-beach-sand-mining-operations-with-new-land-acquisitions/125154757?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-199477/125154757.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "ED arrests businessman in sand mining scam in West Bengal", "para": "The Enforcement Directorate has taken a bold step in the battle against sand smuggling in West Bengal, arresting businessman Arun Sharaf, who leads GD Mining Company. Facing grave accusations of illegal sand mining and money laundering, officers uncovered that his company had been operating beyond sanctioned extraction limits.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/ed-arrests-businessman-in-sand-mining-scam/125154635?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-32780/125154635.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}]}